name: ToxicGarden.finance SEED
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.
The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en:
What is the project about?
Algorithmic stablecoin

What makes your project unique?
Stablecoin 4.0.  We have improved the protocol, adding new vesting and exchange opportunities to reach users. In addition, a powerful DAO fund that can sustain the project.

History of your project.
toxicdeer.finance. DEER is stablecoin pegged USDC.

What’s next for your project?
Toxicgardent.finance. 

What can your token be used for?
SEED pegged to ARB. The protocol is designed to expand and contract supply similar to the way central banks trade fiscal debt to stabilize purchasing power, without any rebases or collateral risk.
